---
import PageLayout from "../../layouts/PageLayout.astro";
import { getTranslation } from "../../utils/i18n";

const lang = "en";
const t = getTranslation(lang);
---

<PageLayout
  title="About Aunova - Long-Term Systems Partner"
  description="Aunova was founded on the belief that the next era of technology will not be defined by more software, but by better systems that protect people and respect the planet."
  lang={lang}
>
  <section class="about-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero-content">
        <h1>{t.about.title}</h1>
        <p class="lead">
          Long-term systems partner for human- and planet-critical infrastructure
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="why-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="why-content">
        <h2>{t.whyAunova.title}</h2>
        <div class="body-text">
          {t.whyAunova.body.map((paragraph) => (
            <p>{paragraph}</p>
          ))}
        </div>
        <aside class="credibility-box">
          <p>{t.whyAunova.credibility}</p>
        </aside>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="principles-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Our Principles</h2>
      <div class="principles-grid">
        <div class="principle-card">
          <div class="principle-icon">
            <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle>
              <path d="M12 6v6l4 2"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Long-Term Thinking</h3>
          <p>We build for 10+ year horizons, designing systems meant to endure and evolve.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="principle-card">
          <div class="principle-icon">
            <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path>
              <circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"></circle>
              <path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"></path>
              <path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Selective Partnerships</h3>
          <p>We engage with a limited number of partners to protect depth, responsibility, and system integrity.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="principle-card">
          <div class="principle-icon">
            <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Human & Planetary Impact</h3>
          <p>We work in domains where technology directly shapes human wellbeing and planetary outcomes.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="principle-card">
          <div class="principle-icon">
            <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <polygon points="12 2 2 7 12 12 22 7 12 2"></polygon>
              <polyline points="2 17 12 22 22 17"></polyline>
              <polyline points="2 12 12 17 22 12"></polyline>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Shared Infrastructure</h3>
          <p>Systems we build become shared assets, designed for the ecosystems they serve.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="approach-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="approach-content">
        <h2>Our Approach</h2>
        <div class="approach-text">
          <p>
            We are not a software vendor. We are long-term systems partners, co-building foundational 
            digital infrastructure for domains where failure has real human or environmental consequences.
          </p>
          <p>
            We do not begin with requirements documents. We begin with strategic alignment. Our partnerships 
            are structured around building systems that become shared assetsâ€”infrastructure that serves not 
            just our partners, but the ecosystems they operate within.
          </p>
          <p>
            We engage selectively, build for decades, and design systems meant to become shared layers 
            within the worlds they serve.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-content">
        <h2>{t.contact.title}</h2>
        <p>{t.contact.intro}</p>
        <div class="cta-actions">
          <a href={`/${lang}/contact`} class="btn btn-primary">{t.hero.cta.primary}</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</PageLayout>

<style>
  .about-hero {
    padding: var(--space-3xl) 0;
    background: linear-gradient(
      135deg,
      var(--color-background) 0%,
      color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-secondary) 10%, var(--color-background)) 100%
    );
  }

  .hero-content {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .hero-content h1 {
    font-size: var(--text-4xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .lead {
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .why-section {
    padding: var(--space-5xl) 0;
    background-color: var(--color-background);
  }

  .why-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .why-content h2 {
    font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .body-text {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-md);
  }

  .body-text p {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .credibility-box {
    margin-top: var(--space-xl);
    padding: var(--space-lg);
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-primary) 5%, var(--color-background));
    border-left: 4px solid var(--color-primary);
    border-radius: 0 var(--radius-md) var(--radius-md) 0;
  }

  .credibility-box p {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .principles-section {
    padding: var(--space-5xl) 0;
    background-color: var(--color-background-elevated, var(--color-white));
  }

  .principles-section h2 {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .principles-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .principle-card {
    text-align: center;
    padding: var(--space-xl);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    transition: all var(--transition-base);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    background: var(--color-background);
  }

  .principle-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-primary);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
  }

  .principle-icon {
    display: inline-flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    width: 80px;
    height: 80px;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary) 0%, var(--color-burgundy-light) 100%);
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
    color: var(--color-white);
  }

  .principle-card h3 {
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .principle-card p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .approach-section {
    padding: var(--space-5xl) 0;
    background-color: var(--color-background);
  }

  .approach-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .approach-content h2 {
    font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .approach-text {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-md);
  }

  .approach-text p {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .cta-section {
    padding: var(--space-5xl) 0;
    background: linear-gradient(
      135deg,
      color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-primary) 5%, var(--color-background)) 0%,
      var(--color-background) 100%
    );
  }

  .cta-content {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .cta-content h2 {
    font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .cta-content p {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .cta-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: var(--space-md) var(--space-2xl);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    transition: all var(--transition-fast);
    text-decoration: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    border: 2px solid transparent;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background-color: var(--color-primary);
    color: var(--color-white);
    border-color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    background-color: var(--color-primary-hover);
    border-color: var(--color-primary-hover);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
    text-decoration: none;
    color: var(--color-white);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero-content h1 {
      font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    }

    .principles-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .why-section,
    .principles-section,
    .approach-section,
    .cta-section {
      padding: var(--space-3xl) 0;
    }
  }
</style>
